;\">Cancel + Restart</span>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"branch-item branch-active\">\n          <span>✓ Active / Working</span>\n          <span style=\"color:#666; font-weight:400; margin-left:2px;\">→</span>\n          <span style=\"color:#93c5fd;\">Continue looping</span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"flow-arrow\">→</div>\n\n    <!-- Decision: Criteria & Review -->\n    <div class=\"decision-center\">\n      <div class=\"decision-box\">Criteria Met<br>&amp; Review Passed?</div>\n      <div class=\"branch-row\">\n        <div class=\"branch-item branch-yes\">\n          <span>✓ Yes</span>\n          <span style=\"color:#666; font-weight:400; margin-left:2px;\">→</span>\n          <span style=\"color:#6ee7b7;\">Halt (Success)</span>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"branch-item branch-no\">\n          <span>✗ No</span>\n          <span style=\"color:#666; font-weight:400; margin-left:2px;\">→</span>\n          <span style=\"color:#fbbf24;\">Resume &amp; Fix</span>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"branch-item branch-dead\">\n          <span>×2 Same bug</span>\n          <span style=\"color:#666; font-weight:400; margin-left:2px;\">→</span>\n          <span style=\"color:#f87171;\">Deadlock Arbitration</span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- Down arrow -->\n  <div class=\"flow-arrow down\">↩</div>\n\n  <!-- ROW 3: Fix / Restart paths -->\n  <div class=\"flow-row\">\n    <div class=\"flow-step\">\n      <div class=\"flow-box fix\">Resume &amp; Fix<br>/codex:rescue --resume</div>\n      <div class=\"flow-sub\">下达修复指令</div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"flow-arrow\">→</div>\n    <div class=\"flow-step\">\n      <div class=\"flow-box deadlock\">Deadlock Arbitration<br>Re-evaluate Architecture</div>\n      <div class=\"flow-sub\">重新评估核心设计</div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"flow-arrow\">→</div>\n    <div class=\"flow-step\">\n      <div class=\"flow-box restart\">Restart Subagent<br>New Strategy